ConfigurationOption.Value: select wo.wonum, wo.description, wo.location, l.description locdescription, wo.assetnum, (select to_char( dbms_lob.substr(ldtext,3999) ) from longdescription where ldkey = wo.workorderid and ldownertable = 'WORKORDER' and ldownercol = 'DESCRIPTION') ldtext, wo.status, wo.wopriority, wo.worktype, wo.parent, wo.lead, wo.supervisor, wo.reportdate, wo.actstart, wo.actfinish, wo.siteid, wo.workorderid from workorder wo left join locations l on wo.siteid = l.siteid and wo.location = l.location where wo.orgid = 'LBNL' and wo.siteid = 'FAC' and wo.istask = 0 and wo.historyflag = 1 and wo.actfinish >= (sysdate - 365)

List.ListEntry: wo.assetnum in ( select assetnum from workorder where ( wonum in (select lbl.refwo from lbl_labtrans lbl where lbl.lbl_transtype = 'PLAN' and lbl.laborcode = '${MX_LABOR_CODE}' ) ) and status in ( select value from synonymdomain where domainid = 'WOSTATUS' and maxvalue in ('APPR','INPRG') ) )

wo.location in ( select location from workorder where ( wonum in ( select lbl.refwo from lbl_labtrans lbl where lbl.lbl_transtype = 'PLAN' and lbl.laborcode = '${MX_LABOR_CODE}' ) ) and status in ( select value from synonymdomain where domainid = 'WOSTATUS' and maxvalue in ('APPR','INPRG') ) )
